    "longBusinessSummary": "Lix Detergent Joint Stock Company manufactures and trades in synthetic cleansers, cosmetics, and chemicals in Vietnam, Cambodia, Japan, Thailand, and the Philippines. The company provides powder, pods, color safe, liquid, and laundry detergents; dishwashing liquids; fabric softeners; bathroom and toilet, kitchen, glass, floor, and all-purpose cleaners; cosmetics; multi-insect killers; air freshener; and sanitizer, perfume, hand wash, scented soap, and shampoos and shower gels under the LIX, On1, Iron & Stone, and Bondy Care brand names. It is also involved in the import and export activities, and the real estate business. The company was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. Lix Detergent Joint Stock Company is a subsidiary of Vietnam National Chemical Group.",
